title: Flowmaster 2015 Dodge Challenger SRT Exhaust Valve Actuator Install Procedure
description: This video covers the proper procedure for re-installation of the factory exhaust valve actuators on Flowmaster's American Thunder and Outlaw Cat-back exhaust systems for the 2015 Dodge Challenger SRT 392, R/T Scat Pack with 6.4L engine, and SRT Hellcat with 6.2L engine. (Flowmaster part #817740 and part #817739)
